.Sh HISTORY
.Nm
was intended to be a
.Nx
replacement for
.Nm efibootmgr
in Linux.
The later is required by
.Nm grub-install
in the
.Nm grub
package.
As a result, the interface is the same with a few exceptions.
For
.Nm
to be used with
.Nm grub-install
it obviously needs to be renamed or linked to
.Nm efibootmgr .
